data/*.sqlite3
data/*.db
khipu/**/*.ndjson

# DEV A gap-closure (2026-06-30): reverse-imported SZLHOLDINGS/immune Space is a
# Node app whose deployable IS its built dist/. Re-include this ONE governed snapshot
# (see spaces/immune/PROVENANCE.md) while the repo-wide `dist/` ignore stays for real
# local build output. The committed dist/data is the shipped SEED ledger; the live
# Space appends to it at runtime, so live divergence there is expected runtime state.
!spaces/immune/dist/
!spaces/immune/dist/**
